{
  "schemaVersion": "1.0",
  "id": "nasty-3btn",
  "label": "Nasty 3-Button Comp",
  "_doc": [
    "Three-button compressor — Light / Medium / Smashed.",
    "No knobs. Each button snaps every internal parameter to a vetted preset.",
    "Built 2026-04-27 in response to UX problem: 10-knob auto-UI was creating",
    "more confusion than control. Three buttons cannot be misconfigured.",
    "",
    "TOPOLOGY (mirrors TOY_COMP exactly): textbook 5-op compressor.",
    "  in ─► detector ─► envelope ─► gainComputer ─► gain.gainMod (sidechain)",
    "       │                                        │",
    "       └─► gain ───────────────────────────────┴─► makeup ─► out",
    "",
    "PRESETS rationale:",
    "  LIGHT   — gentle 2-3 dB GR, slow attack lets transients pass, soft knee",
    "  MEDIUM  — classic 4-6 dB GR, balanced for full mixes / drum bus",
    "  SMASHED — heavy 10+ dB GR, fast attack, hard ratio, NY/parallel territory"
  ],
  "canvas": { "width": 600, "height": 240 },
  "terminals": [
    { "id": "in",  "kind": "input",  "x":  40, "y": 120 },
    { "id": "out", "kind": "output", "x": 560, "y": 120 }
  ],
  "nodes": [
    { "id": "n_det",    "op": "detector",     "x": 180, "y":  60,
      "params": { "mode": "peak" } },
    { "id": "n_env",    "op": "envelope",     "x": 320, "y":  60,
      "params": { "attack": 5, "release": 200, "amount": 1, "offset": 0 } },
    { "id": "n_comp",   "op": "gainComputer", "x": 460, "y":  60,
      "params": { "thresholdDb": -18, "ratio": 4, "kneeDb": 6 } },
    { "id": "n_vca",    "op": "gain",         "x": 360, "y": 180,
      "params": { "gainDb": 0 } },
    { "id": "n_makeup", "op": "gain",         "x": 480, "y": 180,
      "params": { "gainDb": 5 } }
  ],
  "wires": [
    { "from": "in",       "to": "n_det" },
    { "from": "n_det",    "to": "n_env" },
    { "from": "n_env",    "to": "n_comp" },
    { "from": "n_comp",   "to": "n_vca.gainMod" },
    { "from": "in",       "to": "n_vca" },
    { "from": "n_vca",    "to": "n_makeup" },
    { "from": "n_makeup", "to": "out" }
  ],
  "feedback": [],
  "legendOps": ["detector", "envelope", "gainComputer", "gain"],
  "presets": [
    {
      "id": "light",
      "label": "LIGHT",
      "params": {
        "n_env__attack":      10,
        "n_env__release":     300,
        "n_env__amount":      1,
        "n_env__offset":      0,
        "n_comp__thresholdDb": -22,
        "n_comp__ratio":      3,
        "n_comp__kneeDb":     6,
        "n_vca__gainDb":      0,
        "n_makeup__gainDb":   4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "medium",
      "label": "MEDIUM",
      "params": {
        "n_env__attack":      3,
        "n_env__release":     150,
        "n_env__amount":      1,
        "n_env__offset":      0,
        "n_comp__thresholdDb": -24,
        "n_comp__ratio":      5,
        "n_comp__kneeDb":     3,
        "n_vca__gainDb":      0,
        "n_makeup__gainDb":   7
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "smashed",
      "label": "SMASHED",
      "params": {
        "n_env__attack":      1,
        "n_env__release":     80,
        "n_env__amount":      1,
        "n_env__offset":      0,
        "n_comp__thresholdDb": -28,
        "n_comp__ratio":      8,
        "n_comp__kneeDb":     2,
        "n_vca__gainDb":      0,
        "n_makeup__gainDb":   10
      }
    }
  ],
  "ui": {
    "mode": "presets-only",
    "defaultPreset": "medium",
    "_doc_userKnobs": "Whitelist of APVTS param IDs that remain user-facing as knobs (in addition to preset buttons). Everything else is locked.",
    "userKnobs": [
      { "paramId": "n_makeup__gainDb", "label": "TRIM" }
    ]
  }
}
